Print the ptblank_multiagent object

Source: R/print.R
print.ptblank_multiagent.Rd

This function will allow the multiagent object to print a useful HTML-based report.

Usage

# S3 method for class 'ptblank_multiagent'
print(x, view = interactive(), ...)

Arguments

x

An object of class ptblank_multiagent.

view

The value for print()s browse argument.

...

Any additional parameters.
